{"type":"message","id":"9fbc017b","parentId":"5752f46e","timestamp":"2026-03-07T08:05:22.801Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神问得好！本王来给你说说怎么解决飞书token超限的问题：\n\n## 🔧 飞书 Token 超限解决方案\n\n### 1. 调整本王的输出方式\n- 本王以后在飞书那边发消息时，会注意控制字数，少发大段文字和多张图片\n- 心跳巡检的报告，本王以后会简化，或者只在飞书发简版，详细版发webchat\n\n### 2. 飞书插件本身的配置？\n不过本王刚才看了一下，那个报错是飞书OpenAPI的限制：`Total tokens of image and text exceed max message tokens`，这个是飞书平台的硬性限制，不是插件能改的配置。\n\n### 3. 分流方案\n- **简单对话/日常闲聊** → 用飞书\n- **需要发长文、多张图、心跳巡检** → 用webchat\n\n你看这样行吗？或者你有别的想法？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":115346,"output":216,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118946,"cost":{"input":0.0000115346,"output":4.32e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000115778}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772870705104}}
{"type":"message","id":"3840d33c","parentId":"9fbc017b","timestamp":"2026-03-07T08:06:03.971Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-07 16:06 GMT+8] 飞书插件怎么更新"}],"timestamp":1772870763959}}
{"type":"message","id":"a3be5bb5","parentId":"3840d33c","timestamp":"2026-03-07T08:06:20.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神，飞书插件更新的话，用 `clawhub` 命令就行！\n\n## 🦐 飞书插件更新步骤\n\n```bash\n# 先看看已安装的插件列表\nclawhub list\n\n# 更新飞书插件（假设插件名是 feishu-openclaw-plugin）\nclawhub update feishu-openclaw-plugin\n```\n\n不过刚才那个 token 超限的问题不是插件版本的问题，是飞书 OpenAPI 本身的消息长度限制，本王调整一下输出方式就好了～\n\n对了，你要更新插件的话，先看看当前插件列表，确认一下插件名！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":115667,"output":142,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119193,"cost":{"input":0.0000115667,"output":2.84e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000115951}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772870763969}}
